Memberships
Thank you for your interest
in becoming a member at Sawgrass Marriott’s Cabana Beach Club! At this time we are accepting new members. Please contact us to schedule your tour!
Learn about all of the membership exclusives at Cabana Beach Club in Ponte Vedra Beach, featuring everything from private beach access to a beachfront pool. Don’t limit lifelong memories to a vacation. Cabana Beach Club at Sawgrass Marriott Golf Resort & Spa invites you and your loved ones to escape to a holiday state-of-mind every day of the week. Rich in tradition and laced with history, our exclusive club on Ponte Vedra Beach will make you a part of our legacy while pampering you and your family with:
Family Membership
Single Membership
Senior Membership
